# **Evidence Pack (Attach Lean, Highâ€‘Signal Exhibits)**

- Cooperation Log. Short table of offers, dates, outcomes (1â€“2 pages).
- Incident Ledger. Date â†’ behavior observed â†’ child impact â†’ document anchor.
- Thirdâ€‘Party Anchors. School notes, attendance, clinician summaries, exchange receipts.
- Communication Extracts. Platform screenshots limited to logistics; highlight relevant lines.
- Calendar View. One page/month marking actual parenting time vs. order.

