# **Filing Microâ€‘Blocks (Copy/Paste into Motions or Declarations)**

1. Childâ€‘First Framing (Intro Paragraph)
â€œThis request is limited to measures that stabilize the childâ€™s schooling, therapy, and transitions. No relief is sought that would reduce the other parentâ€™s meaningful contact.â€
2. Materiality Screen (Before Allegations)
â€œPetitioner includes only material events affecting safety, schooling, health, or courtâ€‘ordered time. Minor lapses without child impact are excluded or noted as cured.â€
3. Deviation Acknowledgment
â€œPetitioner acknowledges the deviation on [date] due to [reason]. Notice was sent via [platform] at [time]. A cure was proposed and implemented [details].â€
