5. Narrow Tailoring Statement
â€œRequested relief is narrowly tailored to the specific issue and timeâ€‘limited for 60 days with a status review.â€

# **Hearing Day Script (Pocket Version)**

1. Lead with childâ€™s routine. â€œSchool, therapy, exchanges remain unchanged under our proposal.â€
